{"tid":130992,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"ambient music真係好撚正","createTime":"2017-02-22T18:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T01:53:26.000Z","uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"025871256233a0c21dd93fc74912afe9685b718c","tid":130992,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:26:58.000Z","msg":"氛圍音樂（Ambient music），現代音樂的一個分支。又譯為氣氛音樂、環境音樂、視覺音樂或低調音樂。相比於傳統的曲式結構和旋律，此音樂更著重於音色與氛圍的表現。氛圍音樂擁有一種環境的，視覺的， 或者不被人察覺的品質。氛圍音樂的先驅之一Brian Eno認為，氛圍音樂必須滿足各個聽覺注意力層次，不能只強調某一個特定的層次； 也必須既能讓人忽略它的存在，但又非常的有趣。<br />\n氛圍音樂起源於英國，當時像合成器一類全新的音樂合成設備大範圍出現在市面上。從20世紀70年代開始，氛圍音樂以試驗性的，針對當時的合成器的形式為基礎開始不斷發展。Tangerine Dream, Cluster，和作曲家Erik Satie的作品，以及心理聲樂音景系列 Irv Teibel's Environment, 都對氛圍音樂的出現產生了影響。在1978年，Brian Eno通過他的具有里程碑意義的專輯」Ambient 1: Music for Airports「提出了氛圍音樂的概念並進行了推廣。 The Orb and Aphex Twin在20世紀90年代通過他們的氛圍音樂曲目獲得了商業成功。氛圍音樂作品相比於流行的、商業化音樂，大多更加冗長。(quote from wiki)<br />\n<br />\nBrian Eno - An Ending (Ascent)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=It4WxQ6dnn0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIt4WxQ6dnn0&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUytr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=4db72575\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=It4WxQ6dnn0</a><br />\n<br />\nBrian Eno - Deep Blue Day<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yu3mNKpJLgc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dyu3mNKpJLgc&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUytr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=80033752\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yu3mNKpJLgc</a><br />\n<br />\nStars Of The Lid - Don't Bother They're Here<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h1mpNE-2EBo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dh1mpNE-2EBo&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUytr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=4f0bb4c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h1mpNE-2EBo</a><br />\n<br />\nPiano Aquieu - Stars of the lid<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZkKYTvSPzNs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZkKYTvSPzNs&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUytr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=6786224b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZkKYTvSPzNs</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b27ad0675564e469bb0baae8d8e307b70234950","tid":130992,"uid":84615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5c70cde16fbc8acda730a61465cdbb7478ce12","tid":130992,"uid":84615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:31:44.000Z","msg":"訓先會聽<br />\n平時就Citypop比較多"},{"pid":"a9f2b2f9328105553feddba736c8dfb9eada07be","tid":130992,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:34:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓先會聽<br />\n平時就Citypop比較多</blockquote><br />\n我無論做野定訓唔著都會聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a24956e3399574ff9b4ff2841998ecc6db690c2","tid":130992,"uid":84615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:36:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>訓先會聽<br />\n平時就Citypop比較多</blockquote><br />\n我無論做野定訓唔著都會聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽太多D種音樂對人有負作用"},{"pid":"9e2bbf4dabb3b5d630028aa36329e0e49423cc8e","tid":130992,"uid":84615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:39:03.000Z","msg":"你覺得咩係音樂"},{"pid":"560bfdbb02aabfd1ce4318e9acd818c4fdc1e931","tid":130992,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你覺得咩係音樂</blockquote><br />\n個人認為咩都可以係音樂<br />\n好似john cage玩4'33'咁,音樂既定義可以好闊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a87afb341f94e9f6922c6ee0294ed29ebb142a","tid":130992,"uid":84615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score